OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChina jails US citizen, 78,
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor spying                 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Chinese court has sentenced a        
OL,6, 78-year-old US citizen to life in      
OL,7, prison on spying charges.              
OL,9,FJohn Shing-Wan Leung, who is a         
OL,10,Fpermanent resident in Hong Kong, was   
OL,11,Fjailed on Monday.                      
OL,13,FThe court in the south-eastern city of 
OL,14,FSuzhou gave no further details of the  
OL,15,Fallegations against him.               
OL,17,FLeung was arrested in the city two     
OL,18,Fyears ago by a local bureau of China's 
OL,19,Fcounterintelligence agency, a news     
OL,20,Frelease from the court said.           
